    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has been really well-cared for over the years. It's the perfect reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. I've loved every mile in it, and I'm sure you will too\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
