    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry perform with precision. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal, addressing common M96 vulnerabilities. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors for superior thermal management during spirited driving. A mechanically sorted example with a documented service file and a clean DME report.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
